top_stories.title: Apple’s upgraded AI models underwhelm on performance
top_stories.description: Apple has announced updates to the AI models that power its suite of Apple Intelligence features across iOS, macOS, and more. But according to the company's own benchmarks, the models underperform older models from rival tech firms including OpenAI.
top_stories.author: Kyle Wiggers

top_stories.title: Enterprise AI startup Glean lands a $7.2B valuation
top_stories.description: Glean announced on Tuesday that is raised a $150 million Series F led by Wellington Management at a $7.2 billion valuation.
top_stories.author: Julie Bort

top_stories.title: At WWDC 2025, Apple sang developers’ praises amid AI letdowns and App Store battles
top_stories.description: Apple has yet to deliver on some of the key technology advances that could modernize developers' apps for the AI era.
top_stories.author: Sarah Perez

top_stories.title: Report: Meta taps Scale AI’s Alexandr Wang to join new ‘superintelligence’ lab
top_stories.description: Mark Zuckerberg is hand-picking top researchers and engineers to join an upcoming  AI research lab dedicated to “superintelligence," and Scale AI's Alexandr Wang is on the list.
top_stories.author: Rebecca Bellan

top_stories.title: ChatGPT is having a partial outage
top_stories.description: OpenAI experienced a partial outage on Tuesday morning that created some issues for users trying to access ChatGPT, Sora, and the API, the company said on its status page. top_stories.author: Maxwell Zeff
